Revhead MULTi9 (c) Creative Pudding Hungary Llc

Release Date: 12/2017 Protection: Steam
Discs: 1 Genre: Action

Revhead is a car racing simulation game, where you have to build
your own race car. You have a friend Charlie, who is busy with
building race cars. He would need some help from you and he invites
you to Australia. You start your journey somewhere in a small town
in Australia, where the only way to get recognised if you are able
to build the fastest and best racing car around

For more info go to: http://store.steampowered.com/app/589760/

1. Extract release
2. Mount ISO
3. Install the game
4. Copy crack from the PLAZA folder
5. Play!
